Studio Ghibli style illustration of a cozy bedroom at night, warm lamplight casting a golden glow over a parent sitting on the edge of a child's bed holding an open storybook, while twin children nestle under quilted blankets with wide curious eyes. Floating dreamlike above them, whimsical translucent visions emerge from the book's pages - a blue bear sailing a tiny ship, a medieval robber with a feathered hat, mysterious jungle ruins, and a castle drifting among clouds. The room has soft worn wooden floors, scattered well-loved books, and a window showing a starry Singapore skyline in the distance. Magical sparkles and gentle wisps connect the story visions to the children's imaginations. Warm amber and soft blue color palette with delicate brushwork and that signature Ghibli sense of wonder and domestic warmth.
